  "title": "Marine Service Engineer | Training Provided | Diploma | 5 Days | Up To $4K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Marine Service Engineer </strong><br />Salary: Basic $2,000 - $2,800 + OT + Allowances (Gross Salary $3,000 - $4,000)<br />Working Days : 5 days (Monday - Friday)<br />Working Hours : 8am - 5pm<br />Working Location: On board ship</p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct periodic inspections, repair, service and maintenance of marine equipment to ensure reliable</li><li>operation.</li><li>Collaborate with clients and superintendents to deliver quality services efficiently.</li><li>Generate reports and present findings to relevant personnel.</li><li>Provide remote troubleshooting support through emails, ensuring customer issues are resolved promptly to maintain high satisfaction levels.</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Engineering or equivalent (Electrical/Electronics/Mechanical/Mechatronics).</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
